      <p><strong>Other Major Cities:</strong> Bulawayo (~700k, Zimbabwe's second-largest city and a major industrial and cultural centre, known as the 'City of Kings') · Mutare (~200k, situated in the eastern highlands near the border with Mozambique, known for its stunning natural scenery) · Gweru (~150k, located in central Zimbabwe, an important commercial and industrial city known as the 'City of Progress')</p>

