      <p><strong>Demographics:</strong> Arab-Amazigh 99%, European less than 1%. Note: Although almost all Algerians are Amazigh (Berber) in origin and not Arab, only a minority identify themselves as primarily Amazigh, about 15% of the total population.</p>
